24:04.360 --> 24:06.800
even with a particular chapter, but with time markers.

24:06.800 --> 24:09.240
And I love the idea of a sound bite

24:09.240 --> 24:11.640
tag that kind of identifies to the podcast player

24:11.640 --> 24:14.240
