24:14.240 --> 24:17.120
sound bite if you'd like to listen to a bit from the show.

24:17.120 --> 24:18.160
I think that's awesome.

24:18.160 --> 24:20.280
I wish we've had that for years.

24:20.280 --> 24:23.400
And that's just like two of a bunch of really good ideas

24:23.400 --> 24:24.160
that are in there.

24:24.160 --> 24:28.440
