46:24.040 --> 46:27.360
And the phase three namespace was the most recent one

46:27.360 --> 46:29.400
that was fully closed.

46:29.400 --> 46:32.520
And the alternate enclosure tag is

46:32.520 --> 46:37.240
a way to specify multiple enclosures in a single episode

46:37.240 --> 46:41.000
