47:20.840 --> 47:23.640
OK, I'll switch over to the Ogg format.

47:23.640 --> 47:27.680
And it allows it to do intelligent auto changing

47:27.680 --> 47:30.680
to the listeners what their listener wants without having

47:30.680 --> 47:33.200
